{"id":232956349,"title":"我的頭髮被燙壞.....","content":"如題 開始紀錄悲傷歷程...\n是去年8/30在學校附近的被燙壞的 我去這家沙龍都有紀錄時間\n幫我操作的設計師還是評論說不錯的\n到今年一月 我也不知道怎麼辦 我每天看著一大坨剪不完的頭髮\n先上原本一共全頭燙離子燙經過兩次 正常的頭髮\nhttps://i.imgur.com/jfZhs4n.jpg\n\n到爆掉的這次（20190830）\n我是全頭又在第三次離子燙\n髮尾還加燙捲 這張是剛燙完https://i.imgur.com/egbC78r.jpg\n\n後續過沒多久 頭髮變差\n我十月覺得不對勁 去其他家染時 先給設計師看\n他說這是嚴重燙壞 於是討論後先剪一批\n過一段時間的狀況 底下幾乎死光 非常難整理\nhttps://i.imgur.com/pDmv6Wp.jpg\n\n目前左邊的還有一大堆 還是再剪過的\n如圖（頭上有綁頭髮 讓受損最大的部分方便拍）\nhttps://i.imgur.com/LFN2H1w.jpg\n放大後\nhttps://i.imgur.com/QC9StBc.jpg\n\n我每天看這一堆 我真的快瘋掉了\n我真的不知道怎麼辦 一直剪還是一大堆在那\n除了剪還有其他的辦法嗎 \n做結構護也幾乎完全沒用","excerpt":"如題 開始紀錄悲傷歷程...，是去年8/30在學校附近的被燙壞的 我去這家沙龍都有紀錄時間，幫我操作的設計師還是評論說不錯的，到今年一月 我也不知道怎麼辦 我每天看著一大坨剪不完的頭髮，先上原本一共全","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"62268850-d2b4-4c21-a7a3-26e71702a276","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T13:48:33.507Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T13:49:05.648Z","commentCount":8,"likeCount":20,"tags":[],"topics":["染髮","燙髮","心情"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"美髮","forumAlias":"hairsalon","school":"輔仁大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":19},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/jfZhs4n.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/egbC78r.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/pDmv6Wp.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/LFN2H1w.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/QC9StBc.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"7e506a3c-374f-419b-8ef2-4394c2e43068","url":"https://i.imgur.com/jfZhs4nl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/jfZhs4nl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/jfZhs4nl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-25T13:48:33.507Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T1